Scimitar of the Mistwalker Dmg 10, Dly 25. (D Ra)<br>
Spell: Ice Comet (Wz)<br>
Staff of Forbidden Rites Dmg 25, Dly 50. +9 Wis +50 HP +50 Mana (rog/mnk) <br>
Tobrin's Mystical Eyepatch +15 Wis +15 Int (enc/mag/nec/wiz/cle/shm/dru) <br>
